channel.title: New Java
channel.description:
So heres the problem guys, so for a long time I kept java update 20, everything ran perfect. just recently i downloaded the new update 26 because the update thing kept coming up annoying me, now i cant use any clients or runescape :o
Edit: I failed to mention this isn't JDK. I can compile and run a server source 100% it's just clients :s

item.description:
@Andrew_Ferguson wrote:

Delete the Cache RuneScape installs into your C drive and windows folder and try again, if that doesn’t work try restoring it to before the point you installed the java update (most computers make restore points automatically after major updates.)
